  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091227" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">转动式蹬骨手术器械，用于医疗手术。它由手柄、长臂和工作端所构成。长臂由可转动的外套和内轴组成，工作端与长臂之间构成夹角。该器械与相应的人工蹬骨配套使用，具有手术时不遮挡手术者视线，占据空间小，安装蹬骨方便，易于调整、易于掌握操作方法，操作方法简便等优点。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091227" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The utility model relates to a rotary appliance for stapes operation, which is used for medical operation and is composed of a handle, a long arm and a working end. The long arm is composed of a rotary outer sleeve and an inner shaft, and an included angle is formed between the working end and the long arm. The utility model is matched with a corresponding artificial stapes to use, and has the advantages of little occupation space, convenient installation, easy adjustment, easy operation method control, simple operation method, etc. The utility model can not shield the operator' s eyesight during operation.</p>
  </abstract>
